  {
    "udt_struct_v0": {
      "doc": "Represents a single token sale offer.\\n\\nTwo-role access control:\\n- `admin`: cold key / multisig \\xe2\\x80\\x94 controls upgrade, withdraw, drain, freeze, admin transfer, fee updates\\n- `seller`: hot key \\xe2\\x80\\x94 controls pause, price updates (day-to-day operations)\\n\\nFixed fee model:\\n```text\\nInvestor \\xe2\\x94\\x80\\xe2\\x94\\x80$100\\xe2\\x94\\x80\\xe2\\x94\\x80\\xe2\\x96\\xb6 trade()\\n\\xe2\\x94\\x9c\\xe2\\x94\\x80\\xe2\\x94\\x80 fixed_fee ($5)  \\xe2\\x86\\x92 treasury (processing fee)\\n\\xe2\\x94\\x94\\xe2\\x94\\x80\\xe2\\x94\\x80 remainder ($95) \\xe2\\x86\\x92 company (full capital)\\n```\\n- `fixed_fee = 50_000_000`: $5 USDC per trade (1 USDC = 10^7 stroops)\\n- `fixed_fee = 0`:          no fee, company gets 100%\\n\\nCompliance fields:\\n- `deadline_ledger`: sale closes after this ledger (0 = no deadline)\\n- `min_buy_amount`: minimum trade size in stroops (0 = no minimum)\\n- `max_buy_per_buyer`: cumulative cap per buyer in stroops (0 = no cap)",
      "lib": "",
      "name": "Offer",
      "fields": [
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "admin",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "buy_price",
          "type_": "u32"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "buy_token",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "company",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "deadline_ledger",
          "type_": "u32"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "fixed_fee",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "is_active",
          "type_": "bool"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "max_buy_per_buyer",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "min_buy_amount",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "sell_price",
          "type_": "u32"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "sell_token",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "seller",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "treasury",
          "type_": "address"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Creates the offer. Must be called once.\\nStarts INACTIVE \\xe2\\x80\\x94 seller must call set_active(true) after deposit + SAC setup.\\n\\n`admin`: high-privilege key (upgrade, withdraw, drain, freeze). Ideally multisig/cold.\\n`seller`: operational key (pause, price). Can be same as admin for MVP.\\n`fixed_fee`: flat fee per trade in stroops (e.g., 50_000_000 = $5 USDC). 0 = no fee.\\n`deadline_ledger`: ledger sequence after which trades are rejected (0 = no deadline).\\n`min_buy_amount`: minimum buy_token amount per trade in stroops (0 = no minimum).\\n`max_buy_per_buyer`: cumulative buy_token cap per buyer in stroops (0 = no cap).",
      "name": "create",
      "inputs": [
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "admin",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "seller",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "sell_token",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "buy_token",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "treasury",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "company",
          "type_": "address"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "fixed_fee",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "sell_price",
          "type_": "u32"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "buy_price",
          "type_": "u32"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "deadline_ledger",
          "type_": "u32"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "min_buy_amount",
          "type_": "i128"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
          "name": "max_buy_per_buyer",
          "type_": "i128"
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "result": {
            "ok_type": "void",
            "error_type": {
              "udt": {
                "name": "SaleError"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
